headline: 3 Reasons to Sell FOXA and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: FOX has been on fire lately. In the past six months alone, the company’s stock price has rocketed 42%, reaching $47.34 per share. This was partly due to its solid quarterly results, and the performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
